The paper deals with a fundamental problem in networking applications, specifically in maintaining large-scale distributed networks and performing remote file synchronization. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
